{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The repo\u2019s Compose file lives under `infra/compose`, so the earlier `docker compose ps` failure was just the wrong working directory, not a broken stack. I\u2019m reading the local webapp QA instructions now so I can use the repo\u2019s preferred...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_24", "text": "The repo\u2019s Compose file lives under `infra/compose`, so the earlier `docker compose ps` failure was just the wrong working directory, not a broken stack. I\u2019m reading the local webapp QA instructions now so I can use the repo\u2019s preferred browser flow instead of improvising it.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 50, "prompt_index": 25, "prompt_name": "24 \u2014 Design Tokens and Accessibility Foundation", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T02:20:07-07:00"}
