{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented the design-token and accessibility foundation in commits `6efbe82` and `067a12c`. The required reviewer summary was written to [24-design-tokens-and-accessibility-foundation.summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/prompts/2...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_129", "text": "Implemented the design-token and accessibility foundation in commits `6efbe82` and `067a12c`. The required reviewer summary was written to [24-design-tokens-and-accessibility-foundation.summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/prompts/24-design-tokens-and-accessibility-foundation.summary.md). The main code changes are the new primitive layer in [primitives.tsx](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/shared/ui/primitives.tsx), shared button styling in [buttonStyles.ts](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/shared/ui/buttonStyles.ts), the tokenized stylesheet in [index.css](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/styles/index.css), and route adoption in [HomePage.tsx](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/pages/home/HomePage.tsx) and [SessionWorkspacePage.tsx](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/pages/session/SessionWorkspacePage.tsx).\n\nVerification passed with `npm run format:check`, `npm run lint`, `npm test`, and `npm run build` in `frontend/`. Browser QA also passed with the prompt-24 specs, producing screenshots at `/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-24-home-desktop.png`, `/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-24-workspace-desktop.png`, `/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-24-home-mobile.png`, `/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-24-focus-skip-link.png`, and `/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-24-focus-brand-link.png`. I left the pre-existing yolopilot prompt-log changes untouched.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_contex